{"tid":1869125,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Mad Max :  Wasteland》有望今年開拍","createTime":"2020-02-08T03:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T04:25:53.000Z","uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e84ddd1b32808e640a985a7373f6cb70b09357f","tid":1869125,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:59:38.000Z","msg":"2015 年喬治米勒 (George Miller) 執導的《瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道》(Mad Max: Fury Road) ，找來湯姆哈迪 (Tom Hardy) 演出主角麥斯洛克坦斯蓋 (Max Rockatansky) ，由莎莉賽隆 (Charlize Theron) 飾演新角色芙莉歐莎 (Furiosa) ，精緻且到位的動作設計以及美術，完美詮釋了「末日頹廢」美學，也重新復甦觀眾們對這個末世經典系列的關注，讓更多人期待續集的到來。<br />\n<br />\n如今根據外媒報導，系列第五部電影《瘋狂麥斯：荒蕪大地》(Mad Max: Wasteland) 終於有望將在今年秋天於澳洲正式開拍。<br />\n<br />\n不過，湯姆哈迪與莎莉賽隆是否會回歸系列第五部電影仍未確定，由於湯姆哈迪正拍攝安迪瑟克斯 (Andy Serkis) 執導的《猛毒 2》(Venom 2) ，且喬治米勒預計將在下個月展開電影《三千年的思念》(暫譯，Three Thousand Years of Longing) 拍攝，該片會由伊卓瑞斯艾巴 (Idris Elba) 以及蒂妲絲雲頓 (Tilda Swinton) 主演。"},{"pid":"3627bb8cfcaa052c3a4835e1b7db10f267846418","tid":1869125,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"神作"},{"pid":"c50ceac6f9a20ec20539fd725340ec3e3273f28a","tid":1869125,"uid":49853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:02:49.000Z","msg":"Venom 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac1d7ae973c6f21360caa8c4836ee5ce44e0aba","tid":1869125,"uid":206382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"冇Tom Hardy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8339fc05da6bbc5b2e95a781c432ae255ecdf77","tid":1869125,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"唔係geroge miller拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}